  <name>Touché</name>
  <summary>Multi-touch Gestures</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Easily configure your touchpad and touchscreen multi-touch gestures using Touchégg with this GTK graphical user interface.</p>
    <p>For example, you can swipe up with 3 fingers to maximize a window or swipe left with 4 finger to switch to the next desktop.</p>
    <p>Many more actions and gestures are available and everything is easily configurable.</p>
  </description>
